al Stadium]]   \n|location= [[Nilphamari]] \n|attendance=\n|referee= Bharat Chandra Gour\n|result=W\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round=7\n|date= 5 April 2020 \n|time= \n|team1= Chittagong Abahani  \n|score=\n|report=\n|team2= [[Uttar Baridhara SC]]  \n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium= [[MA Aziz Stadium]]  \n|location= [[Chittagong]] \n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round=8\n|date= 8 April 2020 \n|time= \n|team1= Chittagong Abahani  \n|score=\n|report=\n|team2= [[Bangladesh Police FC]]  \n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium= [[MA Aziz Stadium]]\n|location= [[Chittagong]] \n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round=9\n|date= 11 April 2020 \n|time= \n|team1= Chittagong Abahani  \n|score=\n|report=\n|team2= [[Brothers Union]]  \n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium= [[MA Aziz Stadium]]\n|location= [[Chittagong]] \n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round=10\n|date= 21 April 2020 \n|time= \n|team1= [[Rahmatganj MFS]] \n|score=\n|report=\n|team2= Chittagong Abahani  \n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium= [[Bangabandhu National Stadium]]   \n|location= [[Dhaka]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=\n}}\n {{Football box collapsible\n|round=11\n|date= 25 April 2020 \n|time= \n|team1= Chittagong Abahani  \n|score=\n|report=\n|team2= [[Dhaka Mohammedan]]  \n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium= [[MA Aziz Stadium]]\n|location= [[Chittagong]] \n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round=12\n|date= 8 May 2020\n|time= \n|team1= [[Muktijoddha Sangsad KC]] \n|score=\n|report=\n|team2= Chittagong Abahani  \n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium=\n|location=\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|round=13\n|date= 19 May 2020\n|time= \n|team1= Chittagong Abahani  \n|score=\n|report=\n|team2= [[Sheikh Jamal Dhanmondi Club|Sheikh Jamal DC]]     \n|goals1=\n|goals2=\n|stadium= [[MA Aziz Stadium]]\n|location= [[Chittagong]] \n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=\n}}\n{{Fo